sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Student Activity Calendar Management Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open activity calendar management page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW-->>UI: Render student search form

    User->>UI: Search student by username/id
    UI->>LW: searchStudent()
    LW->>DB: Query student and related profile
    alt Found
        DB-->>LW: Student record
        LW->>DB: Query current activity calendar events
        DB-->>LW: Existing events
        LW-->>UI: Render editable activity event list
    else Not found
        DB-->>LW: No record
        LW-->>UI: Error toast
    end

    User->>UI: Save event changes
    UI->>LW: save()
    LW->>DB: Upsert submitted activity events
    DB-->>LW: Persist completed
    LW-->>UI: Success toast
